! Random Color Scheme - Black Background
*foreground:        #a8e3f2
*background:        #000000
*.foreground:       #a8e3f2
*.background:       #000000
emacs*foreground:   #a8e3f2
emacs*background:   #000000
URxvt*foreground:   #a8e3f2
XTerm*foreground:   #a8e3f2
UXTerm*foreground:  #a8e3f2
URxvt*background:   [100]#000000
XTerm*background:   #000000
UXTerm*background:  #000000
URxvt*cursorColor:  #ff6b9d
XTerm*cursorColor:  #ff6b9d
UXTerm*cursorColor: #ff6b9d
URxvt*borderColor:  [100]#000000

! Colors 0-15.
*.color0:  #1a0f2e
*color0:   #1a0f2e
*.color1:  #ff3366
*color1:   #ff3366
*.color2:  #2ecc71
*color2:   #2ecc71
*.color3:  #f39c12
*color3:   #f39c12
*.color4:  #3498db
*color4:   #3498db
*.color5:  #9b59b6
*color5:   #9b59b6
*.color6:  #1abc9c
*color6:   #1abc9c
*.color7:  #ecf0f1
*color7:   #ecf0f1
*.color8:  #7f8c8d
*color8:   #7f8c8d
*.color9:  #e74c3c
*color9:   #e74c3c
*.color10: #27ae60
*color10:  #27ae60
*.color11: #f1c40f
*color11:  #f1c40f
*.color12: #5dade2
*color12:  #5dade2
*.color13: #af7ac5
