*.color66: #34495e
*color66:  #34495e

XClock*foreground: #a8e3f2
XClock*background: #000000
XClock*majorColor:  rgba:a8/e3/f2/ff
XClock*minorColor:  rgba:a8/e3/f2/ff
XClock*hourColor:   rgba:a8/e3/f2/ff
XClock*minuteColor: rgba:a8/e3/f2/ff
XClock*secondColor: rgba:a8/e3/f2/ff

URxvt*depth: 32
